{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1725110492.566058", "card_id": "Q_665790183", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 443}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "男子入职 2 天拒绝周末加班被辞退，耗时 1 年多与公司连打 5 场官司全赢，如何从法律角度解读？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "小伙入职两天因拒绝周末加班被辞退，耗时 1 年多与公司连打 5 场官司全赢，公司从一开始的嚣张到主动求和解。小伙表示这五场官司全部打完，总共经过了一年零四个月，虽然花费的时间比较长，但是最后的结果还是比较满意。（洪观新闻） 男子入职 2 天拒绝周末加班被辞退，耗时 1 年多与公司连打 5 场官司全赢"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-5993e646072ecbe18f24698b51d97f7c_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "840 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665790183"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI0tPf4c3prLx3EAMaCTExMDIzMTA1MiD+ncq2BjAAOPAHQAByCTY2NTc5MDE4M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1725110492.567011", "card_id": "Q_665693306", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "一瓶没开封的矿泉水放十年会变成什么样子？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-38e7f1f77eaec713c9d6e3744b605e10_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "445 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665693306"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0tPf4c3prLx3EAMaCTExMDIwOTMyMSDZ+sS2BjAAOEBAAXIJNjY1NjkzMzA2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1725110492.567388", "card_id": "Q_661210634", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 234}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你听过「故意缩短使用寿命」的设计吗，你身边哪些东西有这个嫌疑？"}, "excerpt_area"